#: controlTypes\state.py:194
msgid "overflowing"
msgstr "бһӣбһҫбһҹбһҖбҹҶбһҺбһҸбҹӢ"

#. Translators: a state that denotes that the object is unlocked (such as an unlocked cell in a protected
