#. in the Create Portable NVDA dialog.
#: gui\installerGui.py:711
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Please specify the absolute path where the portable copy should be created. It must start with a drive letter (e.g. C:). It may include system variables (e.g. %temp%, %homepath%) as placeholders for parts of the path.\n"
