#. it appears in the context of the mirror server group on the Add-on Store page of NVDA's settings.
#: gui\settingsDialogs.py:954 gui\settingsDialogs.py:3791
msgid "Change..."
msgstr "бһ•бҹ’бһӣбһ¶бһҹбҹӢбһ”бҹ’бһҠбһјбһҡбҹ”.."

